Description: edX E-Commerce API Client  |Travis|_ |Coveralls|_
        =================================================
        .. |Travis| image:: https://travis-ci.org/edx/ecommerce-api-client.svg?branch=master
        .. _Travis: https://travis-ci.org/edx/ecommerce-api-client
        
